title: Released version v0.3
message:
Released version v0.3

* Added GPS logging feature
* Added Remote HTTP Prbm upload
* Added Image Capture Feature (Issue #7)
* Fixed bug with Long Press (Issue #5)
* Added 'Other' Category (Issue #2)
* Added 'Building' Category (Issue #3)
* Fixed a bug with number parsing causing crashing (Issue #1)
* Updating of Android build tools and gradle plugin version
